               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla ʾƎsṭifānos za-Gunda Gunde “Vita of ʾƎsṭifānos of Gunda Gunde”
                     (fols. 3ra-52rb)
 II) Malkǝʾa ʾƎsṭifānos za-Gunda Gunde “Image of
                     ʾƎsṭifānos of Gunda Gunde” (fols. 52va-54vb l.7)
 III) Taʾammǝra ʾƎsṭifānos
                     za-Gunda Gunde “Miracles of ʾƎsṭifānos of Gunda Gunde – 9 miracles (fols. 54vb
                     l.8-59va l.4)
 IV) Salām–hymn for ʾƎsṭifānos of Gunda Gunde (fol. 59va
                     l.4-22), incomplete (?), only the beginning
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
