                                 31v</locus> መስከረም: <locus target="#32v">fol. 32v</locus> ጥቅምት:
                                 <locus target="#36r">fol. 36r</locus> ኅዳር: <locus target="#38v">fol. 38v</locus> ዘታኅሣሥምት: <locus target="#36r">fol. 36r</locus>
                              ኅዳር: <locus target="#43r">fol. 43r</locus>.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
